body_html:
Yes, that is what I got as well, because of what I wrote after:
"However, this will not work either ..."

If you run the inspecting graphs script you see that all output nodes are IdentityOp which are removed by the quantize graph script (I think (?)).

Maybe try your luck with transform_graph:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms#inspecting-graphs
Which unfortunately also has an issue posted:
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/44832492/tensorflow-ssd-mobilenet-model-accuracy-drop-after-quantization-using-transform

Let me know if you solve it!

Best
